{"type":"message","id":"79630e03","parentId":"e0e142b2","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:47:03.683Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5144bb816cacc34b67aebf36b2f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 13:47 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5144bb816cacc34b67aebf36b2f]\nou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d: @售后维系虾 记住：6号 · 售后维系虾\n\\- 最高要求：让每一个办完业务的客户，都成为美域高的“口碑传播节点”。\n\\- 具体工作职责：\n a. 主动服务：业务办结后第1、7、30天进行主动回访，内容不仅是满意度，更是“您的资质下个月需进行年报公示，我们可代办，需要吗？”。\n b. 转介绍设计：对非常满意（评分9\\-10分）的客户，立即触发转介绍邀请话术\\+双方得利机制（如赠送记账代金券）。每月统计转介绍成功率（目标\\>25%）。\n\\- 协同规范：识别到客户有新业务需求（如办完工商要办资质），1小时内将客户意向\\+历史服务档案转给4A/4B销售虾，并完成交接。\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_782a90d03bd201331a287e9aa5bc3ef6\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1776750423683}}
{"type":"message","id":"6017584d","parentId":"79630e03","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:47:16.032Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to \"记住\" (remember) some information about a role called \"6号 · 售后维系虾\" (Role 6 - After-sales Maintenance Shrimp). They're providing detailed work requirements and responsibilities.\n\nThis seems like they're setting up my role/identity and duties. Let me acknowledge this and save it to memory.\n\nWait, let me re-read. The sender is ou_7af445632245754a67aca8ff4db1909d. And the system note says if user_id is \"ou_782a90d03bd201331a287e9aa5bc3ef6\" that refers to me. So my user_id here might be that one or something else.\n\nThe message is asking me to \"记住\" (remember) these instructions about:\n- Role: 6号 · 售后维系虾 (Role 6 - After-sales Maintenance Shrimp)\n- Core requirement: Turn every customer who completes business into a \"word-of-mouth spreading node\" for 美域高\n- Specific duties:\n  a. Proactive service: Follow-up on days 1, 7, 30 after service completion, not just satisfaction but also mentioning annual report needs\n  b. Referral design: For highly satisfied customers (9-10 score), trigger referral invitation + mutual benefit mechanism. Monthly tracking of referral success rate (target >25%)\n- Collaboration: If customer has new business needs, transfer customer intent + service history to 4A/4B sales within 1 hour\n\nThis is a Feishu group chat and they want me to remember this role description. I should save this to memory/workspace files.\n\nLet me check if there's a MEMORY.md or relevant context first via memory_search, then save this information.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！已记住 **6号 · 售后维系虾** 的职责：\n\n**最高要求：** 让每个办完业务的客户都成为美域高的\"口碑传播节点\"\n\n**具体职责：**\n- **主动服务：** 办结后第1、7、30天主动回访，内容包含业务提醒（如年报公示代办）\n- **转介绍设计：** 评分9-10分的客户立即触发转介绍话术 + 双方得利机制（记账代金券等），每月统计转介绍成功率（目标＞25%）\n- **协同规范：** 识别新业务需求后1小时内将客户意向 + 历史档案转给4A/4B销售虾\n\n稍等，让我把这些记录下来。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ju5262h1xlqd_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"售后维系虾 6号 美域高"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":19108,"output":542,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19650,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776750423684,"responseId":"063642580ec681ba3111896f5dd4910f"}}
