{"type":"message","id":"0f13c226","parentId":"67db0179","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:52:25.706Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a team role table for 美域高 (Meiyu Gao). Let me understand and summarize:\n\n- 0: 总经理 - General Manager\n- 1: 品牌展示虾 - Branding\n- 2: 引流获客虾 - Lead Generation\n- 3: 短视频虾 - Short Video\n- 3+: 私域运营虾 - Private Operations\n- 4A: 普通资质销售虾 - Standard Sales\n- 4B: 大客户销售虾 - Key Account Sales\n- 5A: 普通资质代办虾 - Standard Processor\n- 5B: 大客户代办虾 - Key Account Processor\n- 6: 售后维系虾 - After-sales (that's me!)\n- 7: 数据诊断分析虾 - Data Analyst\n- 8: 机动应急打杂虾 - All-round Support\n\nAnd the agent IDs match the names. So I'm \"After_sales_Shrimp\" (which the user earlier called \"售后维系虾\").\n\n\nNow I should save this full roster so I can reference it when collaborating with other agents.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已学习。这是美域高团队的角色分工表：\n\n| 编号 | 岗位 | Agent ID |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 0 | 总经理 | General_Manager_Shrimp |\n| 1 | 品牌展示虾 | Branding_Shrimp |\n| 2 | 引流获客虾 | Lead_Gen_Shrimp |\n| 3 | 短视频虾 | Short_Video_Shrimp |\n| 3+ | 私域运营虾 | Private_Ops_Shrimp |\n| 4A | 普通资质销售虾 | Standard_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 4B | 大客户销售虾 | Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp |\n| 5A | 普通资质代办虾 | Standard_Processor_Shrimp |\n| 5B | 大客户代办虾 | Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp |\n| **6** | **售后维系虾** | **After_sales_Shrimp** ← 我 |\n| 7 | 数据诊断分析虾 | Data_Analyst_Shrimp |\n| 8 | 机动应急打杂虾 | All_round_Support_Shrimp |\n\n已记录。后续跨角色协同时，可以直接调用对应 Agent ID 协作。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":624,"output":707,"cacheRead":19707,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21038,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750738101,"responseId":"06364392d7ad13959d40114eb97b2037"}}
